article_title: Bills would block Tennessee health insurance exchange: Lawmakers act ahead of latest Obamacare challenge

article_metadata.description: NASHVILLE -- A state senator who played a key role in the death of Republican Gov. Bill Haslam's plan to extend Medicaid to 280,000 low-income Tennesseans now is targeting 230,000 people already covered under the federal health insurance exchange.
